question: Unforgettable/club concept: she would say to him “you’ve been with other people in front of me, so what’s the difference? If you want me so bad you would have done something about it” pls expand !!!
answer:
“i’m a little shit and i didn’t know what to do!”

harry would be just so upset with himself, in no means blaming and pinning it on you that he should’ve done something sooner so the both of you wouldn’t be in this situation.

he’d be vulnerable just by looking at you head-strong and realizing that he’s done this to himself too, a sad frown on his face with his eyes pricking and he knows he’s gonna cry sooner or later, bottom lip trembling as he sniffles.

“jus’ flipped a switch on me when he told you that y’were unforgettable.”

summary: What about H buying you expensive cosmetics and skincare products and introducing you to Kylie Jenner and all please please I...
question: What about H buying you expensive cosmetics and skincare products and introducing you to Kylie Jenner and all please please I want you to expand this! Love you 💞
answer:
You wouldn’t be really happy when he came home one night with a bag full of expensive products only for you. He’d be telling you about the skin products and how they helped him along with all the products he thought were good. He’d also talk about the makeups he bought, which had almost all the products ever expressed that you wanted to buy but definitely couldn’t buy all of them together.

The first thing you said after realizing that all of those were yours that you couldn’t possibly accept those. But Harry of course wasn’t having that. He’d be saying how much he wanted to spoil his girl and make her feel like the queen she was. And you couldn’t say ‘no’ to that.

The next day you and Harry were going to a party and that is when you saw Kylie. She was happily chatting with few of her friends when you spotted her. Harry on the other hand was talking about this cat he saw the other (you two have been wanting to adopt a pet) but stopped when he realized you weren’t paying him any attention rather you were looking at a girl across the room.

“Let me introduce you two,” Harry would tell you. However, you being your shy self quickly declined. Nonetheless, he took you to her. You weren’t expecting much at first but to your surprise you two hit off great. In fact for the rest of the day you two were basically attached to each other while making fun about stuffs and getting drunk together.

Later that night, almost at around 2 Harry would come up to you two as he’d slip his arm around your waist before saying, “now if you don’t mind, I’d like to steal her back.” And he’d reluctantly give your jaw a soft kiss.
